Apart from being a successful model slash entrepreneur, Blac Chyna also happens to be a singer, performer and a mother of two.The 33 year old Hollywood socialite recently dropped a new single and fans are really excited about it. Fans took to Twitter to say;

I’m loving Blac Chyna as a music artist! I’m getting my life!I don’t know why I’ve had Blac Chyna’s Hollywood song in my head lately. It’s catchy lol. 

However, we were quick to note that this new hit also seems to be hinting at her troubles in Hollywood and in the entertainment industry.Chyna’s newest single is all about the model’s glamorous world of Los Angeles and her possible new love interest. Here are some of the lyrics from her new song, Hollywood:

There’s a shy boy lives on my street. He called me movies star. Got me a bougie pair of dark sunglasses. Wear ‘em till the sun goes down on the car. Drivin’ to Hollywood. I wish I could stay. Drivin’ to Hollywood. Get out of the way.

Throughout the video, Chyna is seen driving around town with pink and colorful outfits and with a new man on her mind. While this music video doesn’t call out the Kardashians directly, Chyna does give out some hints throughout the music video.Chyna has also sprinkled in some inspirational messages in her song to let everyone know that she’s okay despite all the legal lawsuits surrounding her. Some of these messages include:

Never stop dreaming and live colorfully.

The music video also ends on a questionable note. By the end of the music video, we see Chyna park her car and walk away from the scene while someone opens the door to the passenger’s side of the car. And at the end, we get a “to be continued” message on screen.Could this be a sign that Chyna is planning on leaving Hollywood once the lawsuits are over? Or maybe it’s a sign that the mother of two still has a few surprises left for the Kardashian-Jenner clan.While we wait for the part two of Chyna’s video, let’s look at how the beef between Chyna and the Kardashians started.

According to Chyna’s personal attorney, the Kardashian family has been on a mission to destroy Chyna’s career. As you all know, Rob and Chyna created a spin off show from the KUWTK show. This new spin-off show focuses on Rob and Chyna’s lives. The show had a good following and lots of memorable moments for the two but was suddenly cancelled by Entertainment Tonight.Chyna went ahead to file a lawsuit against the production team and the network claiming that it was Kris Jenner who ultimately pulled the plug on the reality show.The second season of Rob and Chyna which did not air was especially important to Chyna since it showed the couple in a much better light. From working on their relationship together to taking care of their daughter, Dream, Chyna demanded the release of the footage for the public to see. 

Among Chyna’s allegations is a claim that Kris Jenner, Kim Kardashian, Khloe Kardashian and Kylie Jenner secretly defamed Chyna and illegally interfered with Chyna’s highly lucrative content with the E! Network/NBCUniversal. Their alleged illegal interference caused the cancellation of Rob & Chyna. Bunim/Murray must produce the unaired season 2 of Rob & Chyna and KUWTK footage to Chyna within 45 days. The judge also ruled that unaired footage from KUWTK filmed in March 2017 must also be handed over. The unaired KUWTK footage shows Chyna and Rob working on their relationship and co-parenting their daughter, Dream Kardashian.

Chyna seems to be winning the court cases against the Kardashian-Jenner clan since three judges are already siding with her.Her attorney continued to reveal that:

The evidence reportedly corroborated Chyna’s claim that Kris Jenner who is often called a momager, lied about an accusation that Chyna beat the s* out of Rob’s face, then used that alleged fabrication to get the show canceled.
